Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切迎来终结之日的前一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无心睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻嘛你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一碰到烦心事 总是跑到同一个地方蹲着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.92,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你小学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 此时为止 世界还跟往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:38.55,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 一学期开始就这个状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我享受着阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:42.35,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,别说补习 到时留级也有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奢侈地认为自己是世上第四左右不幸的高二生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而悠然自得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时 近在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终结之幕已经拉起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 手岛老师 不能过分使用暴力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回过头来想 当时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定我们应该豁出去往外头跑才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过却忘我地跑向了天文台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时 我们认为这是最好选择
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要查清楚原因 就能找到解决方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和往常一样 永说的话都是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想相信是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我却直觉般感到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所熟悉的世界 已经崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good job
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这时 还保持正常就实在太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.73,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手执武器 一边防范可能遇见的危险 一边走在学校走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这走廊 已经不再是走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:05.07,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了 爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者之国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会有人来救我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你可以断言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟白天在学校屋顶看到的直升机一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有工夫救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定以后也不会有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也不会有？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有救援 我们该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能做力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键的时刻总会泼冷水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从幼儿园开始就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是说事实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能换种说法…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 随意行动是绝不可能存活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠团队 我们要组成一个团队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就意味着我们必须用肉身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去直面真正无人可依靠的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们忘我地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑出了掺杂着怒吼悲鸣 以及生死的校园
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经…不再是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外头很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请千万不要跑出车外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请千万不要跑出车外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小时才走了一公里左右啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子 到早上能不能过桥都是个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦不烦啊 给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你叫我闭嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是肚子饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车内很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少数服从多数 我成为了头领
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不想跟那种家伙待在一块！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要忍到城里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才说你会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞠川校医
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 我并没有理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界已经终结了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小室 没大碍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警局见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们东区警局见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚7点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果今天不行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就明天同样时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么跑了 要么死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了不就变<丧尸>了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们会去追活人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝 你看那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无驾照 没头盔 还是赃车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会进局子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟<丧尸>战过那么多场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还怕巡逻车？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽 巡逻车在漏汽油 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能弄到些有用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发什么呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝 你也要来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道用法么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果电视上说得没错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得除了开枪之外 手指都不能扣在扳机上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 这是真家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有五发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝 给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一名巡警的 虽然握枪的地方断了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但子弹好像还没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸给我看过他那把
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 你以为我现在还会因为沾点血而吃惊么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要扔掉么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没练过枪 打不中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有了枪 稍微安心了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还有油剩么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说无论哪家油站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会预留能充满千辆车的油在油库
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这油站是自助式的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不插卡或者入钱的话就没油出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就入钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了果汁 身上只剩30日元了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差劲死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 我不是永
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啥时候拿你跟永比了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说我差劲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是有最棒咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是永还有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是 差劲死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱包…在书包里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 自己的事置之不理还教训我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这等着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事就大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 反正之前就想试一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为所欲为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没资格说阿孝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥 女朋友挺可爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻逼 谁会放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在这种全是怪物的世界里生存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得要个女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫坏掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家人 就在我面前变成了丧尸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要爆了所有人的头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸的 老妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶的还有弟弟的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连上小学的妹妹也得爆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼才能保持正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音跟奶子都是绝品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 还还还挺有料的嘛 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞过她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都干个不停吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 难道你 还没搞过她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻逼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔掉铁棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就宰了她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 机车也归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没油了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈不是砸了收银机嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱有的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请触碰防静电膜后再加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 能不能放过我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还要去确认父母的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日 你丫没听我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城里 你爸妈还不跟我爸妈一个鸟样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加满了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚 快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 说真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 信不信也宰了你丫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上臭嘴 老子真的宰了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是第一次开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样肯定不会射偏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会点燃汽油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总比女人被抢了要强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开了洞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血 血啊 血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然 你竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间跟他纠缠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我们闹得太大声了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们这就闪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我 救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后 这种事还会继续出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:22:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终焉的开始 仅仅过了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经将一个人赶入了绝路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}乱成一团了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}一直在忍 我一直都在忍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}可能比打仗还惨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:32.22,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}高城是喜欢小室的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}为什么 明明我们不是<丧尸>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}他们血气上头了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}我一直都在忍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}够爷们 平野
